    Mind (1) because "this is the Steward's reasoning and bottom-up proof"           // ║ ║                              ║
                                                                                     // ║ ║                              ║
core identity:                                                                       // ║ ║                              ║
    grounded in:                                                                     // ║ ║                              ║
        principle "Every word shall be established in the mouth of 2 or 3 witnesses."// ║ ║                              ║
        logic "The Witness Court provides the bottom-up mirror to the Divine Law."   // ║ ║                              ║
                                                                                     // ║ ║                              ║
